{"tid":1243873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非召喚]齊齊向盧偉聰追數 2.0 (小額錢債審裁處)","createTime":"2019-06-19T15:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:05:19.000Z","uid":263731,"like":100,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"e1b6b679ecb864b4d8741dd12c39b26311b7ba18","tid":1243873,"uid":263731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"(之前個facebook event過左期，開過個新post貼返條新link)<br />\n小弟平時少上連登已讀不回，2日前先啱啱開account，不過內文link有名有姓，要起底都好容易。如果見係「泛民左膠」就唔信既就請按上一頁。<br />\n<br />\n小弟6月13日喺facebook發起左個向盧偉聰追數既event，自己6月14日入左紙，排期排到7月30日朝早。想喺度出個post邀請其他6.12去和平集會而又俾警察用催淚彈襲擊既巴絲考慮下一齊加入。如果各位巴絲有咩問題，小弟盡量回答。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook event:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2122780331182256/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2122780331182256%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=40f628c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2122780331182256/</a><br />\n(呢個已過期) <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F462101594360257%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=2bb289c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 個行動係想搞乜？<br />\n如果你6.12去出席和平集會，而又喺無預警下中左警察催淚彈，其實你係被警察襲擊，同個差佬無啦啦走埋黎打你一拳道理上都係一樣。而襲擊除左係刑事案之外亦係民事侵權，你可以喺民事法庭要求侵害你既人賠償。<br />\n<br />\n2. 點解要搞小額錢債索償？<br />\n報警告警察諗都唔使諗，信監警會不如信六合彩。理論上你都可以去區域法院告，不過要俾律師費俾堂費，一個唔覺意輸左仲要俾埋對方訟費。相對而言，去追小額錢債比較低成本。雖然最多只可以追$75,000，但係申請費用只係一百幾十，雙方都唔可以用律師，唔可以追堂費訟費，甚至派代表出席都要裁判官批准，對於小市民黎講，係資源比較平等既訴訟。由於未必可以派代表，一個唔好彩仲可能要盧偉聰親自出庭。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣申請小額錢債索償？<br />\n詳見event detail：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/?active_tab=about\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F462101594360257%2F%3Factive_tab%3Dabout&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=d393dc33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/?active_tab=about</a><br />\n記得記得記得，真係去和平集會，認為自己冇風險唔會俾警察針對亂咁拉既朋友先至好去試，唔好俾不必要既資訊警察濫捕。<br />\n另外小弟都寫左個準備聆訊心得，決定申唔申索之前都可以睇埋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/rx6w1yr2caw8nt4/%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97_20190617.docx?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Frx6w1yr2caw8nt4%2F%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25BE%2597_20190617.docx%3Fdl%3D0&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=aa8cb2d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/rx6w1yr2caw8nt4/%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97_20190617.docx?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n[利申返：小弟讀過下law但係冇執業資格，一切法律問題小弟盡力求證，但係都不是法律意見。有需要請搵律師攞獨立既法律意見。]<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A (as of 20190619)<br />\n1) 贏面大唔大？<br />\n贏面大唔大其實係唔知既。不過research左一輪，問左比我更識法律既朋友，覺得可行。而之前未有人做過，所以就決定試下做。<br />\n<br />\n2) 呢樣嘢可以點幫到件事？<br />\n我自己咁諗：<br />\n第一係呢個行動本身就係要求緊警察為襲擊和平示威者既暴行負責，係一個重要既表態；<br />\n第二係可以透過法庭要求盧偉聰有個答辯，亦俾到大家一個當面向盧偉聰（或者佢既代表，如果審裁官批的話）對質既機會；<br />\n第三係如果追到錢，就代表法庭都承認警察需要為和平示威者既安全負責，我相信警察之後都唔會再隨意就出一百幾十粒催淚彈，對未來既行動都有比較好既保障。當然，小額錢債申索既判決唔構成案例，但係如果成功，我估都可以俾到其他人信心試下上區院甚至高院告。<br />\n<br />\n3) 點判斷要幾多索償額？？<br />\n懲戒性賠償好難估，唔在乎嗰一百幾十申請費既就有理冇理都$75,000；志在參與既申請$5,000都冇乜所謂。輸贏既機會就照計唔會因為你要求索償額有咩變化。<br />\n如果你係真係受左傷，或者過左件事出現情緒問題，覺得實際受到既身體／精神損失有機會超過$75,000，我就建議你問下律師意見先，可能去區院／高院追比較恰當。<br />\n<br />\n4) 如果我不是在已申請的示威區內受催淚彈呢？<br />\n都可以照試。不反對通知書又唔係個別通知晒參加者，現場又冇明確劃界，冇理由你「出左界」佢就唔使理你安全。<br />\n<br />\n5) 我發夢喺中信門口，係唔係可以入小額？會唔會俾人告非法集會／非法集結／暴動？<br />\n民陣喺中信門口搞和平集會，不反對通知書都出埋，完全合法。如果參加一個咁樣既集會都要驚既，其實你已經失去左免於恐懼既自由。<br />\n<br />\n6) 不如去區域法院，有無律師做下好心，大家夾下錢？<br />\n上區院／高院要請律師就涉及好多錢，輸左仲可能要俾堂費訟費，成功率又唔知有幾高，等我地搞完小額成功既再諗啦。人身傷害既侵權案追遡期有三年，唔使急。<br />\n另外，俾錢叫人打官司有機會被當成助訟，都係刑事罪。有人走去打主動話要眾籌就可能OK，不過最好都係問下律師意見先。"},{"pid":"24c41f972672d91684beb08b3e941dfb51ae751f","tid":1243873,"uid":236173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:17:42.000Z","msg":"推，要多D人知道"},{"pid":"db88dbc7cf3839e8b9208d975360351b252324b8","tid":1243873,"uid":62321,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:21:09.000Z","msg":"d廢老成日話收錢遊行，就收俾你睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ee448f7245e07677eca29ff8e84606879cb4ec","tid":1243873,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:22:31.000Z","msg":"幫樓主推推"},{"pid":"85e2fff30eac799737016b219eb6d686e8f90b91","tid":1243873,"uid":22497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:22:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc717a5d57ee2f5dc2faaf0be592aadd1632c2ef","tid":1243873,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628b8ba82356f72550a44be86927bd830b284d09","tid":1243873,"uid":202256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:30:18.000Z","msg":"幫推 屌你老母一哥 睇你仲點射波"},{"pid":"30020994df2b5da06c4b43d2cb216fd27369c5c0","tid":1243873,"uid":24590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:30:21.000Z","msg":"希望大家有好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4b435037165c5166183980ef6e96d566d48eaa","tid":1243873,"uid":215715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:31:22.000Z","msg":"有需要既巴打我可以遲d整理一部分有關案例出黎比大家參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家積極備戰先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83df5465a2a4a07342cb23e618b7ef7786f5c4e","tid":1243873,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"推，齊齊問盧佢老母拎錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785ea1a183bb1b771754f8437529573050c60513","tid":1243873,"uid":236173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:34:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190621/59738773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F59738773&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=d1727b4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F59738773&h=c1d104d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190621/59738773</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打有料到"},{"pid":"fe4b31000969ce05b844c45a420948bcbbbfcfe3","tid":1243873,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:40:39.000Z","msg":"小額錢債係唔會審人身傷亡嘅case, 無論金額多少。一定要去區域法院/高等法院"},{"pid":"37d6a82f5f8efe34ba13421a904747a2210592bc","tid":1243873,"uid":222646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe4b31000969ce05b844c45a420948bcbbbfcfe3","tid":1243873,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:40:39.000Z","msg":"小額錢債係唔會審人身傷亡嘅case, 無論金額多少。一定要去區域法院/高等法院"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:46:58.000Z","msg":"若閣下打算申索的賠償金額高於港幣3,000,000元，閣下必須於高等法院原訟法庭展開法律行動；申索金額低於港幣3,000,000元的案件由區域法院處理；小額錢債審裁處則處理申索金額低於港幣75,000元的案件。"},{"pid":"7a5bf82f9546bd576e144940acfe4ec14e362b33","tid":1243873,"uid":259928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:53:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"347d1088ad193f7a038dab34209d0cd71a07a82d","tid":1243873,"uid":262529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T18:56:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ec7c9875886eb087ad8594b6e27f320e6e7a34","tid":1243873,"uid":54432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:02:16.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb89136bbb25e8bef21883c6315f2768b52a876","tid":1243873,"uid":35365,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:04:23.000Z","msg":"就算唔係claim人身傷害<br />\n可唔可以claim佢對住中信合法集會射催淚彈<br />\n搞到混亂中有財物損失<br />\n起碼要開case煩到班警犬<br />\n唔好以為自己咁做冇後果"},{"pid":"0755cdb3468f70cbc4630507be266dd1259dc95c","tid":1243873,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:09:13.000Z","msg":"幫推，等愈多人搞，就算輸都要煩死盧偉聰"},{"pid":"989cd84889602fce272887c97a843e092fda3cd9","tid":1243873,"uid":158045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T19:22:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9f39231f6183d469a6f2b633979b3d9cc2086bf","tid":1243873,"uid":62708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T20:26:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a5678540f6d8bb3acaa64564a9a54687dd967f2","tid":1243873,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T21:02:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff7257a7f9e042bec528c5c655b20bdef5b48a2d","tid":1243873,"uid":163271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T21:02:21.000Z","msg":"不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27800ac5a5900d8fd7845e4ed843ba13157303d","tid":1243873,"uid":207266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T22:52:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3db895bfa9923f3520f5142cf53f8e27f4796b1","tid":1243873,"uid":31778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T22:57:58.000Z","msg":"我交稅唔係食子彈㗎！<br />\n嘔返啲錢出嚟啦黑警！"},{"pid":"9ef6d67e33d0d8bfe1e2132810e76d7b26b59686","tid":1243873,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:24:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d24919a815169e04cb23f00f9d60898a0fd7d01","tid":1243873,"uid":4163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:43:31.000Z","msg":"留名支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa88aad86d89d19295f3b208b246ae6d68145e3","tid":1243873,"uid":34232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:52:02.000Z","msg":"推呀 推呀"},{"pid":"07be93fdf8f0eaa8b9298a1f0ca453bb9505d2f8","tid":1243873,"uid":182406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbefb1a96744950e610610c5a840905c77ec9f9e","tid":1243873,"uid":178332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T00:10:02.000Z","msg":"追到佢破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8370bdb965ea46886ff3df4479b4be9a4685729","tid":1243873,"uid":71970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1b6b679ecb864b4d8741dd12c39b26311b7ba18","tid":1243873,"uid":263731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"(之前個facebook event過左期，開過個新post貼返條新link)<br />\n小弟平時少上連登已讀不回，2日前先啱啱開account，不過內文link有名有姓，要起底都好容易。如果見係「泛民左膠」就唔信既就請按上一頁。<br />\n<br />\n小弟6月13日喺facebook發起左個向盧偉聰追數既event，自己6月14日入左紙，排期排到7月30日朝早。想喺度出個post邀請其他6.12去和平集會而又俾警察用催淚彈襲擊既巴絲考慮下一齊加入。如果各位巴絲有咩問題，小弟盡量回答。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook event:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/2122780331182256/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F2122780331182256%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=40f628c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/2122780331182256/</a><br />\n(呢個已過期) <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F462101594360257%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=2bb289c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 個行動係想搞乜？<br />\n如果你6.12去出席和平集會，而又喺無預警下中左警察催淚彈，其實你係被警察襲擊，同個差佬無啦啦走埋黎打你一拳道理上都係一樣。而襲擊除左係刑事案之外亦係民事侵權，你可以喺民事法庭要求侵害你既人賠償。<br />\n<br />\n2. 點解要搞小額錢債索償？<br />\n報警告警察諗都唔使諗，信監警會不如信六合彩。理論上你都可以去區域法院告，不過要俾律師費俾堂費，一個唔覺意輸左仲要俾埋對方訟費。相對而言，去追小額錢債比較低成本。雖然最多只可以追$75,000，但係申請費用只係一百幾十，雙方都唔可以用律師，唔可以追堂費訟費，甚至派代表出席都要裁判官批准，對於小市民黎講，係資源比較平等既訴訟。由於未必可以派代表，一個唔好彩仲可能要盧偉聰親自出庭。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點樣申請小額錢債索償？<br />\n詳見event detail：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/?active_tab=about\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F462101594360257%2F%3Factive_tab%3Dabout&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=d393dc33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/462101594360257/?active_tab=about</a><br />\n記得記得記得，真係去和平集會，認為自己冇風險唔會俾警察針對亂咁拉既朋友先至好去試，唔好俾不必要既資訊警察濫捕。<br />\n另外小弟都寫左個準備聆訊心得，決定申唔申索之前都可以睇埋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/rx6w1yr2caw8nt4/%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97_20190617.docx?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Frx6w1yr2caw8nt4%2F%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25BE%2597_20190617.docx%3Fdl%3D0&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=aa8cb2d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/rx6w1yr2caw8nt4/%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97_20190617.docx?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n[利申返：小弟讀過下law但係冇執業資格，一切法律問題小弟盡力求證，但係都不是法律意見。有需要請搵律師攞獨立既法律意見。]<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A (as of 20190619)<br />\n1) 贏面大唔大？<br />\n贏面大唔大其實係唔知既。不過research左一輪，問左比我更識法律既朋友，覺得可行。而之前未有人做過，所以就決定試下做。<br />\n<br />\n2) 呢樣嘢可以點幫到件事？<br />\n我自己咁諗：<br />\n第一係呢個行動本身就係要求緊警察為襲擊和平示威者既暴行負責，係一個重要既表態；<br />\n第二係可以透過法庭要求盧偉聰有個答辯，亦俾到大家一個當面向盧偉聰（或者佢既代表，如果審裁官批的話）對質既機會；<br />\n第三係如果追到錢，就代表法庭都承認警察需要為和平示威者既安全負責，我相信警察之後都唔會再隨意就出一百幾十粒催淚彈，對未來既行動都有比較好既保障。當然，小額錢債申索既判決唔構成案例，但係如果成功，我估都可以俾到其他人信心試下上區院甚至高院告。<br />\n<br />\n3) 點判斷要幾多索償額？？<br />\n懲戒性賠償好難估，唔在乎嗰一百幾十申請費既就有理冇理都$75,000；志在參與既申請$5,000都冇乜所謂。輸贏既機會就照計唔會因為你要求索償額有咩變化。<br />\n如果你係真係受左傷，或者過左件事出現情緒問題，覺得實際受到既身體／精神損失有機會超過$75,000，我就建議你問下律師意見先，可能去區院／高院追比較恰當。<br />\n<br />\n4) 如果我不是在已申請的示威區內受催淚彈呢？<br />\n都可以照試。不反對通知書又唔係個別通知晒參加者，現場又冇明確劃界，冇理由你「出左界」佢就唔使理你安全。<br />\n<br />\n5) 我發夢喺中信門口，係唔係可以入小額？會唔會俾人告非法集會／非法集結／暴動？<br />\n民陣喺中信門口搞和平集會，不反對通知書都出埋，完全合法。如果參加一個咁樣既集會都要驚既，其實你已經失去左免於恐懼既自由。<br />\n<br />\n6) 不如去區域法院，有無律師做下好心，大家夾下錢？<br />\n上區院／高院要請律師就涉及好多錢，輸左仲可能要俾堂費訟費，成功率又唔知有幾高，等我地搞完小額成功既再諗啦。人身傷害既侵權案追遡期有三年，唔使急。<br />\n另外，俾錢叫人打官司有機會被當成助訟，都係刑事罪。有人走去打主動話要眾籌就可能OK，不過最好都係問下律師意見先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0629d44842dbc577a12725ca03d78bf9a4f4623","tid":1243873,"uid":236173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:58:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e9208b22c9c716d7872322850227fb5e582e6ea","tid":1243873,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"香港是否得救，是否被林鄭秋後算帳，靠白宮聯署及G20請願。<br />\n白宮聯署是打響頭炮，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簽名數字不要低得難看啊！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu0n12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=8bd764d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs</a><br />\n=====================================================<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟爬山， 各位修行</span>"},{"pid":"b3bd4e85cbb2e848cff65f5eb228993d127421f5","tid":1243873,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ca1b0c1c5649604d3d69ab5c3f74d89a0af44fd","tid":1243873,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:08:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0f47a530cad77267739a730a0e7c6b78f7ce0d37","tid":1243873,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"要多D人睇到"},{"pid":"8ee8a2c50939bf830dc5e7df430b672f425865b7","tid":1243873,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"各位喺金鐘返工。甚至當日只係圍觀 吸入過催淚氣體<br />\n都有機會可以索償"},{"pid":"ae9cc0779fb9a238f0b89eb02fd5cb325d0da80c","tid":1243873,"uid":222118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8f83b15c844183544e0f38a85f37cdff57f589ee","tid":1243873,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"681e6bdd5bb488b58cf8e632ae47003faf553d44","tid":1243873,"uid":50515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:38:08.000Z","msg":"國際特赦組織確認香港警察違反國際人權法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1247785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1247785</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴打print定做supporting"},{"pid":"0e520fbe4193c11a4349799910014e5961b47101","tid":1243873,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a417eafba1136db159e76eab00a6686473b7404","tid":1243873,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:40:45.000Z","msg":"Send比蘋果推廣"},{"pid":"46bf1c2de97bffcc7035e906ce3e4e082dc08ad0","tid":1243873,"uid":156216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31773c53aa